# Summit Breadcrumb Mini-Nav

Summit pages should use this breadcrumb pattern:

- `MCT Summit EU / <Year City (CC)> : [Summit] | [Agenda] | [Pictures]`

Behavior:

- `MCT Summit EU` links to home.
- `<Year City (CC)>` links to `/<slug>/summit/`.
- `Summit`, `Agenda`, and `Pictures` link to their respective summit pages.
- The active item is highlighted (bold or equivalent emphasis).

Routing expectation:

- Visiting `/<slug>/` should take users to `/<slug>/summit/`.
